### === Row-Level Authorization (Lesson 29) ===

### Step 1: Organizer creates a draft event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events
Authorization: Basic organizer:organizer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Organizer One's Event",
  "startDate": "2026-09-15",
  "endDate": "2026-09-16",
  "maxCapacity": 100
}

### Step 2: Activate the draft → creates the active event
# Replace {{eventId}} with the ID from Step 1
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events(ID={{eventId}},IsActiveEntity=false)/AdminService.draftActivate
Authorization: Basic organizer:organizer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "SideEffectsQualifier": ""
}

### Organizer reads events → sees own event
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events
Authorization: Basic organizer:organizer

### Organizer2 reads events → empty (no events created)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events
Authorization: Basic organizer2:organizer2

### Organizer2 tries to read organizer's event by ID → 404
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events(ID={{eventId}},IsActiveEntity=true)
Authorization: Basic organizer2:organizer2

### Organizer2 tries to edit organizer's event → 403
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events(ID={{eventId}},IsActiveEntity=true)/AdminService.draftEdit
Authorization: Basic organizer2:organizer2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "PreserveChanges": true
}

### Admin reads events → sees all events
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### --- Registration ownership ---

### Attendee registers for an event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/register
Authorization: Basic attendee:attendee
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

### Attendee reads own registrations → sees the registration
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Registrations
Authorization: Basic attendee:attendee

### Attendee registers again for same event → 409 (duplicate)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/register
Authorization: Basic attendee:attendee
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

### Organizer reads registrations → empty (didn't register for anything)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Registrations
Authorization: Basic organizer:organizer